            <p>H. LAW FIRM (恒. 律师事务所) is headquartered at 208-7050 Woodbine Avenue, Markham — in the heart of the GTA's largest Chinese-Canadian community. Miao He leads the firm personally and provides family law services tailored to the cultural and legal needs of Markham's Chinese-Canadian residents.</p>
