            <h2>Family Law Issues Common in Markham</h2>
            <p>Markham Chinese-Canadian families often face family law matters involving cross-border assets, Chinese marriage certificate authentication, and property division spanning both Canada and China. Miao He holds dual licences in Ontario and China, providing a true one-stop service for these complex matters.</p>
          </div>

