              <li>Child Custody &amp; Access — primary residence, parenting time, relocation</li>
              <li>Marriage Contract (Prenuptial Agreement) — protecting parental gifts, pre-immigration property</li>
              <li>Cross-Border Assets — Chinese real estate, offshore accounts, dual-country asset disclosure</li>
              <li>Emergency Motions — asset freezing orders, restraining orders</li>
              <li>Separation Agreement — comprehensive settlement before formal divorce</li>
            </ul>
